transcript:
Customer: Vijay bhai.
Executive: Hello ha ji Sabir bhai.
Customer: Ha ha hum jungle mein hai abhi.
Executive: Jungle ho abhi aap.
Customer: Ha ha to kal subah baat kare.
Executive: Achcha kal subah baat ho payegi kya.
Customer: Ha bas main bas ek hi baat puchni thi wo aapke pass ek madam ka call aaya hoga unko share kar diya sab kuch ho gaya ha.
Executive: Aapne unko approval dal diya hosting ke liye approval unka mere pass sab mera hai.
Customer: Ha sab tak unko bol diya Friday ko karane ke liye live theek hai.
Executive: Kab bolne ke liye live karne ke liye bola aapne unko Friday ko.
Customer: Shukrawar shukrawar ha.
Executive: Shukrawar ko to mere pass itna kehna tha ki kam na sara karwa lena catalog ke andar jo bhi pending kam hai na aapka catalog ke andar.
Customer: Bhaiya shukrawar karane ka zimmevari aapka hai hum aapka zaban pe kam kar rahe hain.
Executive: Nahi wo to theek hai wo theek hai bas main keh raha ki jitne bhi prakar ke aapke.
Customer: Abhi hathi nikal raha hai bhaiya abhi hathi nikal raha hai.
Executive: Kabhi gali ke samne hathi aa jaye pata nahi.
Customer: Kya bol rahe ho.
